---
---
<section class="prob" id="problemas">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="prob__head reveal">
      <p class="prob__eyebrow">O problema</p>
      <h2 class="prob__h2">
        O WhatsApp não foi feito<br/>
        para <span class="gold-text">gerir estúdios.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="prob__sub">A improvisação custa caro. Cada mensagem perdida é um cliente que vai embora.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards grid -->
    <div class="prob__grid" data-stagger>
      <div class="prob__card reveal delay-100">
        <div class="prob__card-num">01</div>
        <div class="prob__card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/><path d="m9 10 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Conversas <span class="gold-text">perdidas</span><br/>e horários esquecidos.</h3>
        <p>Misturar vida pessoal com agendamentos em chat gera caos. Clientes somem porque a mensagem afundou no fluxo.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prob__card reveal delay-200">
        <div class="prob__card-num">02</div>
        <div class="prob__card-icon prob__card-icon--red">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/><path d="m14 14-4 4"/><path d="m10 14 4 4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3><span class="gold-text">Prejuízo</span> com<br/>'No-Shows'.</h3>
        <p>O tempo é seu ativo mais valioso. Um horário vazio por no-show é dinheiro que nunca mais volta — e dói.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prob__card reveal delay-300">
        <div class="prob__card-num">03</div>
        <div class="prob__card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Horas <span class="gold-text">gastas</span> digitando<br/>as mesmas coisas.</h3>
        <p>Orientações de preparo, cuidados pós-tattoo, confirmação de horário — copiar e colar todos os dias é desperdício.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Dashboard screenshot proof -->
    <div class="prob__proof reveal delay-200">
      <div class="prob__proof-label">
        <span class="proof-dot"></span>
        Dashboard InkBook — ao vivo
      </div>
      <div class="prob__screen-wrap">
        <div class="prob__screen-frame">
          <img src="/imagens/Captura de Tela (852).png" alt="Dashboard InkBook com métricas financeiras" class="prob__screen-img" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <!-- Floating metrics -->
        <div class="prob__metric prob__metric--left">
          <span class="metric-val">R$ 1.250</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Receita hoje</span>
        </div>
        <div class="prob__metric prob__metric--right">
          <span class="metric-val">4</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Sessões confirmadas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Garante alinhamento global consistente nesta seção */
  :global(.prob .container) {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 4rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    :global(.prob .container) { padding: 0 2.5rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    :global(.prob .container) { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  }

  .prob {
    background: #060606;
    padding: 10rem 0 8rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prob { padding: 6rem 0; }
  }

  /* Headline */
  .prob__head {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .prob__eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C9A24D;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .prob__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4.5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .prob__sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  /* Cards */
  .prob__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .prob__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .prob__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }
    .prob__card { padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem; }
    .prob__head { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  }

  .prob__card {
    background: #0c0c0c;
    padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .prob__card:hover {
    background: #111;
  }

  .prob__card-num {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .prob__card-icon {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(201,162,77,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,162,77,0.15);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #C9A24D;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .prob__card-icon--red {
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(192,57,43,0.2);
    color: #e74c3c;
  }

  .prob__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .prob__card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  /* Screenshot proof */
  .prob__proof-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .proof-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #27AE60;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(39,174,96,0.6);
    animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  .prob__screen-wrap {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .prob__screen-frame {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .prob__screen-frame:hover {
    transform: perspective(1200px) translateY(-10px);
    border-color: rgba(201,162,77,0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 60px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(201,162,77,0.1);
  }
  .prob__screen-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .prob__metric {
    position: absolute;
    background: rgba(12,12,12,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,162,77,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    animation: floatMetric 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .prob__metric--left { bottom: -1rem; left: -2rem; }
  .prob__metric--right {
    top: -1rem; right: -2rem;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }
  @keyframes floatMetric {
    from { transform: translateY(0); }
    to   { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prob__metric--left { left: 0.5rem; bottom: auto; top: -0.5rem; }
    .prob__metric--right { right: 0.5rem; top: auto; bottom: -0.5rem; }
    .prob__metric { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
    .metric-val { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .prob__metric { display: none; }
  }

  .metric-val {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #C9A24D;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .metric-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
